class="comment-body"><h3>P1h3r1e3d13 says on <a
href="#comment-256042" title="">November 29th, 2007 at 6:59 pm</a></h3><p><p>re: #13:<br
/> Also, I just realized &#8220;browser.cache.disk capacity&#8221; sets the maximum hard drive cache size.  For limiting RAM usage, you want &#8220;browser.cache.memory.capacity&#8221;, which is not settable in Tools&gt;Options.</p></p></div></div><div
