href="#comment-346509" title="">January 27th, 2010 at 6:57 am</a></h3><p><p>Here&#8217;s a simple one that a surprising amount of people don&#8217;t know about.</p><p>Hit the &#8220;ESC&#8221; (Escape) key to &#8220;STOP&#8221; a page from loading. It&#8217;s handy when you click a link by accident, and when you get to pages where the circular loading animation keeps spinning on the page tab. Works in most other browsers too.</p></p></div></div><div
